name: Sterling Silver Curves
description: Hand shaped and hammered sterling silver drops. These look ultra modern and hang beautifully from your ear lobes. Earwires are also sterling silver and handmade.

name: Buttons 'n Pearls
description:
A cool variety of vintage white buttons are grouped for effect on this fun necklace. I just love all the sizes and texture and pearls accent the pretty buttons. It's like wearing a collection on your neck!
Length =

name: Copper Rounds
description: Copper shines in these handmade earrings featuring a pretty, round link. Copper is a beautiful, warm metal that goes well with all gemstones. Here we've paired it with pearls, sea glass beads and turquoise. Fresh ear wires.

name: Fall Romance
description:
Gorgeous gold sari silk ribbon is paired with bronze chain for a nostalgic look. Vintage Czech crystals adorn the chain along with a old fashioned rose drop pendant. This piece is so pretty and romantic!
Length =

name: Aged Crucifix
description:
The patina on this old crucifix is beautiful! It dangles from a gorgeous vintage brooch and complimented with green faceted beads. This is a great statement piece!
Length =

name: Green Sparkle
description: These green Czech glass beads have such a pretty sparkle! I've topped them off with a silver faceted bead. They hang from handmade sterling silver ear wires.

name: Vintage Chandelier Drop
description: I have always loved the gorgeous, faceted drops from old chandeliers. Using them as a pendant is the perfect way to display your love for all things old. This one is paired with a little rhinestone sparkle and hangs on bronze chain.

name: Czech Glass Blue
description: My favorite beads to work with are Czech glass. There is something very special about the cut and color of Czech made beads. These blue vintage glass beads are no exception. They hang from my handmade sterling silver ear wires.

name: Czech Glass Modern
description: There is something very special about Czech glass and they way it catches the light. These glass beads are a beautiful combination of blue and green. My handmade ear wires are sterling silver.

name: Time Key
description:
I love the combination of watch parts and old objects. Here I added a key to bring more whimsy to the necklace. Four handmade wire links and faceted, iridescent bronze crystals compliment the fun, funky pendant. Toggle Closure.
Length = 17.25"

name: Amazonite Briolette
description: Amazonites are my favorite gemstones! They are a beautiful shade of blue/green and look great on everyone. These hang on handmade, sterling silver ear wires along with faceted vintage Czech beads and pearls.

name: Long on Sparkle
description:
These earrings are the perfect "go to" pair for jeans or an evening out. I just love long ear wires! They put standard ear wires to shame. Choose from an assortment of faceted gemstones.
Ear Wire Length (from top to bottom of drop) = 2.5"

name: Skeleton Keys
description:
I love the shape and weight of vintage skeleton keys. Each one with it's own unique shape and they make great pendants! Here are 3 versions with semi precious stones: turquoise, coral and pearls on bronze chain.
Length = 23"

name: Unlock the Past
description:
A cool, old keyhole looks awesome paired with this gorgeous vintage brooch! Together they dangle a pretty gold cross. Pearl accents complete the necklace for a very unique piece.
Length = 18 - 19.5"

name: Time Worn Bling
description:
Vintage rhinestone necklace holds sweet, old charms and objects from the past. An aged watch face is the star along with 2 sweet lockets (oval and heart). Also, a vintage flower earring and some pearls to boot. Very fun necklace!
Length = 17.5"

name: Keyed Up
description:
A cool, antique skeleton key with a rusty patina, is the star of this necklace. We clear sealed the key to maintain it's cool, old appearance. Flanking the key are vintage Czech beads and mother-of-pearl buttons.
Length = 24"

name: Prism Pendant
description:
Vintage prism from an old chandelier sparkles at the end of silver and rhinestone chain. Beautiful, vintage Czech glass beads are featured above. Long necklaces are super fashionable right now and this one looks great with any outfit.
Length = 24"

name: Vintage Button Earrings
description: Mother-of-pearl vintage buttons are showcased on bronze filigree. So fun and very lightweight.

name: Czech Glass Earrings
description: These simple and sweet earrings are made with vintage Czech glass beads. In addition, the silver & pearl are made with vintage silver drops and freshwater pearl. All earrings on sterling silver ear wires.

name: Long Druzies
description:
Long necklaces are all the rage and look great with so many outifts! These gorgeous druzies on chain glitter like stardust! Druzies are crystal covered rocks. Tiny quartz crystals form on the surface or within the cavities of rocks. These are so fun to wear. I get tons of compliments when I sport mine! Also, the gold chain that I chose is a nice antiqued gold (not too shiny).
Length = 28.75"

name: Clearly Druzy
description:
Clear beads highlight a beautiful white druzy complimented with silver chain at the neckline. A druzy is a crystal covered rock. Tiny quartz crystals form on the surface or within the cavities of other rocks. It appears as a coating of glittering stardust!! You will love wearing this statement necklace.
Length = 17.5"
Druzy = 1.5" long

name: Thimble & Button Necklace
description:
A vintage thimble makes for a pretty pendant coordinated with a blue turquoise bead and stack of old buttons. Silver chain and more buttons complete this fun necklace.
Length= 20.5 inches
Pendant Drop= 3 inches

name: Golden Times
description:
A vintage gold watch face in pendant form dangles a watch part and beautiful gold Czech crystal. I've combined gold and silver chain for a funky, steampunk look.
Length = 20"

name: Button Links
description: Beautiful vintage buttons in shades of ivory and white. Available in bronze or silver.

name: Pink Sparkle
description: Gorgeous Czech glass in pretty pink. When the light hits the facets of the glass, they have a gorgeous sparkle! Handmade sterling silver wires make these extra special.

name: Vintage Spool Necklace
description:
Such a fun way to display your love for sewing or quilting! A vintage spool is renewed with beautiful sari silk wrapped around and hung from a silver chain. Dangling underneath is a super cute scissor charm. Pretty faceted beads in gorgeous sea foam and white are hand wrapped to accent the spool pendant.
Length - 22.5 inches
Pendant Drop - 4 inches

name: Simply Elegant
description:
Sweet rhinestone drop is the focal of this lovely pearl necklace. Great for any occasion.
Length=

name: Birthstone Key
description:
Our filigree bronze key has a great vintage look and dangles a pearl plus your birthstone. Checkout the Swarovski crystal birthstone chart for your month. This is also a lovely and affordable gift item! Pictures show March and August birthstones.
Length = 17"

name: Tasseled
description: Cute tasseled earrings with bronze and brass chain featuring gold  and clear crystals.

name: Embellished Cuff
description: Since clocks and time faces are so popular, we took our Time Cuff a step further. Embellished with filigree, crystal and a vintage clock face, this cuff is super cool and unique. Our aged cuff is brass an 2" wide. Do not bend your new cuff. Slip your wrist in gently and your cuff will keeps it's shape forever.

name: Etched Brass Cuffs
description:
Cuffs are all the rage due to their versatility. We hand etch our cuffs in fun motifs and give them a vintage patina. All cuffs are brass and 2" wide.
Note- do not bend your new cuff. Just gently slip on your wrist and it will keep it's shape forever.

name: Bronzed Beauty
description:
Our Bronze Beauty necklace incorporates many elements to create a super stylish necklace. A combination of smoky topaz and Czech glass beads in bronze tones give warmth to a brass flower and chain. A little touch of gorgeous sari silk ribbon completes this necklace.
Length=

name: Double Beauty
description:
Two very beautiful rhinestone flowers are the highlight of this gorgeous necklace. Great for a bride on her wedding day or for anyone for a special occasion. Each flower rhinestone is 1.25" across.
Length=20"
*Can be made shorter or longer.

name: Starburst Rhinestone
description:
Gorgeous vintage rhinestone piece is centered on a beautiful strand of pearls. Perfect for a bride's special day. Rhinestone focal is 1.75" across.
Length= 15.5"-17"
*Can be made longer.

name: Copper Hoops
description: I absolutely love the warmth of copper. It looks great on everyone! These hoops are handmade and adorned with beautiful Czech crystals in a gorgeous pink. French ear wires.

name: Topaz Key Necklace
description:
Beautiful smoky topaz faceted stones compliment an antique skeleton key. We clear sealed this rusty key to maintain it's beautiful patina. Long necklaces are so fashionable and this one looks awesome with any outfit.
Length = 24"

name: Rain Rhinestone
description:
Vintage rhinestone with beautiful movement. Individual strands of rhinestones are graduated and dangle nicely. Gorgeous crystal pearls make this one-of-a kind necklace simply stunning.
Length=17.5"-19"
Can be made shorter or longer

name: Faith Artisan Bracelet
description: Handmade with turquoise beads on beautiful tan leather, pewter cross and chain. Gorgeous mother-of-pearl button closure.

name: Round Rhinestone
description:
A breathtaking vintage rhinestone piece was incorporated with white pearls for a gorgeous, one of a kind necklace. Rhinestone is 1.5" across.
Length = 19-21"
Can be made longer.

name: Vintage Button Bracelets
description: What better way to display a charming collection of vintage buttons than a charm bracelet! These vintage buttons were hand selected to create a fun mix of textures in gold and silver.

name: Fleur Button Necklace
description: A vintage mother-of-pearl button flaunts itself just above coral colored beads and a beautiful seafoam green fabric flower. We think the vintage button adds a little whimsy to the necklace and the color combination is so lovely!

name: Spring Bling Necklaces
description:
Spring is here and what could be more fun than flaunting a beautiful flower necklace! Shabby chic style fabric flowers are front and center in these vintage style necklaces. Beads and bronze chain compliment the pretty pendant. 
Length = 17"

name: Hot Gold Earrings
description: These earrings are hot! They have a sexy dangle that makes them fun for evenings and a fashion statement for daytime with jeans.

name: Urban Wood & Chain Necklace
description:
Cool materials make this piece funky and contemporary. We've joined suede, wood beads and polished gold chain together for this one of a kind statement necklace.
Length=22" with toggle clasp

name: Jasper Bracelets
description:
Jasper stones come in numerous colors and variations. We've taken our favorite large stones and made them the focus of these cool bracelets. These standout with the help of brushed gold chain.
Size= 8" (average size)
*Please let us know if you need a smaller or larger size. We would be happy to make the adjustment.

name: Royal Druzy
description:
Purple is such a royal color and this gorgeous icy white druzy is highlighted with amethyst and purple agate beads. A druzy is a crystal covered rock. Tiny quartz crystals form on the surface or within the cavities of rocks. The crystals are small and look like a coating of glittering stardust!
Length = 18" - 18.5" (extender chain)
Druzy - 1" wide

name: Sweet Vintage Floral
description:
This necklace evokes days gone by. A sweet turquoise blue rose and white pearls are paired with antiqued brass for a feminine statement necklace.
Length= 22" with lobster clasp

name: Filigree Faith Earrings
description:
These sweet filigree crosses are so comfortable and lightweight. A pearl dangle is just the right touch.
Length= hangs 1.5 inches

name: Urbanite Earrings
description:
Simple and sleek! These contemporary earrings give off a very cool vibe with copper and suede.
Length=2.5 inches

name: Rosette Earrings
description:
Turquoise blue roses are highlighted with crystal and pearls. You're sure to receive compliments on these!
Length=hangs 1.25 inches

name: Bohemian Baubles
description:
Our Bohemian Bauble necklace is fashionably long and uses an array of stones. The handmade braid gives it a very earthy vibe.
Length =

name: Hail Mary Earrings
description: I love the Virgin Mary connectors used in the making of rosaries. Why not incorporate them into other jewelry pieces? I used them here as a feature in these pretty earrings with red Czech glass and turquoise beads. Silver base metal.

name: Blooming Roses Necklace
description:
These rose pendants are blooming cute! Silver chain and silver heart charms make these so fun and wearable. 
Length=16.25 to 16.75 inches

name: Party Hoops
description: These fun hoop earrings are a party on earwires! Gold hoops hold black onyx and amber dangles.

name: Floral Heart Necklace
description:
Sweet and girlie! Our heart locket is surrounded with pearls, chain and charms. Add your significant others photo to this locket and carry him close to your heart.
Length = 19 inches, flower/heart drop=2 inches, Toggle clasp.

name: Stone Cold Heart Necklace
description:
Even though you have a warm heart, you can wear our stone cold pendant for fun. Choose between pink/feminine chain or blue/bold chain. These will look great on your neckline with any outfit but a sure thing with jeans.
Length = 16.5 inches with lobster clasp

name: Blue Ice Druzy
description:
This gorgeous icy blue druzy is flanked by small angelite beads and silver chain. A druzy is a crystal covered rock. Tiny quartz crystals form on the surface or within the cavities of rocks. The crystals look like a coating of glittering stardust!
Length = 18.5 - 19.5" (extender chain)
Druzy - 1.25" wide

name: Cool Wrap
description: Our Cool Wrap bracelet makes a fashion statement with freshwater pearls or faceted red beads on leather. Wraps 3-4 times around your wrist with a silver button closure.

name: Festive Filigree Earrings
description: Brass filigree is the show stopper on these pretty earrings. A contemporary but vintage look, complimented with ivory pearl dangles.

name: Cross It Bracelet
description:
A pretty rhinestone cross graces your wrist with a contemporary feel. Crosses are curved to perfectly fit your wrist and are complimented with a matching chain. 
Length = 7.25 inches

name: Faceted Pendant Necklace
description:
Beautiful faceted drop pendant with a modern feel. Stone is framed in matte gold and hangs from a feminine beaded gold chain. A super contemporary necklace with it's simplicity.
Length = 18"

name: Cross Etched Cuff
description:
Our brass cuff is etched with a vintage faith message for a cool wrist adornement. Pretty brass filagree cross with a Swarovski crystal centers the bracelet. Metal is hot this season and looks great with all your outfits!
Cuff width = 1 1/2" x 5 3/4"

name: Cross Love Bracelet
description: Brass link bracelet with lovely brass cross charms. Pearl and Swarovski clear crystals compliment the bracelet.

name: Old World Rosary
description: Great rosary for the man in your life. Beautiful brown 8mm cat's eye Hail Mary beads reflect the light for a nice brown and tan combination of color. Czech crystal in a complimentary shade of gold is used for the Our Father beads. Antique bronze Virgin Mary connector and crucifix.

name: Contemporary Black Rosary
description: Contemporary rosary with black 8mm cat's eye Hail Mary beads. These beautiful beads reflect the light for a lovely black and gray cast. Our Father beads are clear Czech crystal. This rosary is a great man's gift but also appropriate for women. Silver Virgen Mary connector and crucifix.

name: Saint Mary Rosary
description: Crisp white 8mm cat's eye Hail Mary beads look beautiful on this rosary. Clear and sparkly Czech crystal are the Our Father beads. A great gift for a wedding, confirmation or First Holy Communion! Silver Virgin Mary connector and crucifix.

name: Saint Rose Rosary
description: A lovely rosary using 8mm dark pink cat's eye Hail Mary beads. Beautiful cat's eye beads pick up the light and shimmer. Our Father beads are Czech crystal in a complimentary pink. Silver toned Virgin Mary connector and crucifix.

name: Heart Love Bracelet
description: Love the vintage look! Beautiful brass hearts dangle from gold chain. The addition of Swarovski crystals and pearls give this bracelet a very soft, feminine feel. Even though all the components are new, it still evokes the past.

name: Believe Bracelet
description: Artisan handmade bracelet with brown leather, pearls, gold metal chain and cross. Vintage button closure.

name: Wire Wrapped Cross
description:
Each cross is hand wrapped in a free form style using non-tarnish silver wire and beautiful gemstones. Your unique wrapped cross hangs on a leather necklace with lobster clasp closure.
Length= 20 inches

name: Aquatic
description:
Choose from aquatic colors of green and blue dangling from silver link chain. White pearls highlight the faceted beauty of these briolettes. Specify blue or green.
Length: up to 18"

name: St. Peter Rosary
description:
Leopard Jasper beads paired with Riverstone (Our Father beads) are a great combo for a boy's rosary. Sterling silver Jesus connector with components and Riverstone cross. Hail Mary beads are 6mm.
Length:  16"

name: Lucky Charms
description:
I like to think these vintage charms brought individuals from the past good luck! And how could you go wrong with three good fortune charms hanging from one necklace? Heavy gold chain carries a beautiful old crystal, etched locket and sweet rose pendant. 
Length - 18"

name: Pearl Rosary Necklace
description: Show your faith with a beautiful rosary necklace. Pretty sterling silver rosary connector of the Virgin Mary dangles a sterling silver cross and freshwater pearl. Very feminine piece and great gift for weddings, graduations and confirmations.

name: Love Locket
description:
This is the sweetest heart shaped locket I've ever seen! "I Love You" inscribed on the front with a pretty pink rose and added to it, a pink Swarovski crystal. The locket is in great shape and opens up for your special photos. Hanging from sterling silver and pearl chain.
Length:  17" - 18 1/2"

name: Serendipity
description:
A cluster of vintage charms comes together to make a beautiful and unique necklace. The focal point is a lovely pearl and gold brooch flanked with purple crystals, pink and white pearls and a compilation of old charms. A real eye catcher!
Length: 17 1/2"

name: SweetHearts Necklace
description:
Creamy pink pearls and Swarovski crystal make for a sweet necklace. The descending heart trio dangle is made of sterling silver.
Great Valentine's or Mother's Day gift!

name: Cherry Quartz
description: These  faceted cherry quartz gemstones shimmer hanging from handmade, sterling silver ear wires. Accompanied by vintage Czech beads and pearls, these are super pretty.

name: Zen
description:
Cool, green Aventurine gemstone in a faceted, briolette cut dangles inside this perfect circle. Very simple and Zen like style! Gold filled chain shines.
Length: 16-17 1/2"

name: Vintage Grace
description:
Unique vintage cameo is given a fresh look paired with lemon quartz on gold filled chain. The gold detailing around the cameo coordinates beautifully with the brilliance of the quartz. A very regal necklace!
Length: 17" - 18 1/2"

name: Amethyst Rosary
description:
O sing to the LORD a new song; sing to the LORD, all the earth.  Sing to the LORD, bless his name; tell of his salvation from day to day.-Psalm 96

Beautiful keepsake rosary handmade with amethyst gemstones and Swarovski crystal.  All components are sterling silver including the exceptionally detailed Bali butterfly beads handcrafted in Bali, Indonesia.

name: Sunset Trio
description:
The gorgeous colors of sunset are represented in this stunning necklace.  Three tiers of gold filled, wired gemstones featuring a green faceted pendant.
Length: 16 1/2 - 17 1/2"

name: Classy Baubles
description:
Classy cluster of beautiful stones with a vintage feel. Onyx, pearls and gold Swarovski crystals come together on gold filled chain. Great sparkle when light hits this pretty necklace.
Length: 16 - 17 3/4"

name: Knotted & NiceTurquoise
description: Unique tube turquoise is knotted to make a really urban piece.  Be sure to checkout its sister necklace, "Tubular Tuquoise and Leather". They make a great team!

name: Water & Pearl
description:
Lovely fresh water pearls wired on gold filled chain and paired with a Carribean blue pendant.  This blue reminds me of the clear waters of the beach.  Great summer necklace!
Length: 14 3/4 - 16"

name: Pearl Cascade
description:
Freshwater pearls cascade off a sterling silver chain.
The natural shapes of the pearls are beautiful and give this necklace a very organic feel.
Length:  15"

name: Feathered
description:
Gemstone charms in cool shades of orange highlight a sterling silver feather charm to tickle your fancy. Sterling silver chain.
Length: 15 3/4"

name: Green Cat's Eye Rosary
description:
O LORD, our Sovereign, how majestic is your name in all the earth!-Psalm 8

An artful rosary with dark green cat's eye beads (8mm) coordinated with beautiful, large Rainforest Jasper rounds.  Sterling silver Bali spacers and woven-like cross make for a striking piece.

name: Personalized Rosary
description:
A personalized rosary is a perfect gift and keepsake for the special child in your life.  Rosaries make a beautiful gift for Baptism, First Holy Communion or Confirmation. We can customize a rosary in a child's birthstone or favorite colors. Personalization is offered up to 10 letters in sterling silver blocks.  
Please contact me directly to discuss your customization needs.

name: Leopard Skin Jasper Rosary
description:
The LORD is my shepherd, I shall not want. He makes me lie down in green pastures; he leads me beside still waters; he restores my soul.-Psalm 23

Leopard Skin Jasper gemstones are coordinated with handmade accent beads and sterling silver.

name: Gray Pearl Rosary
description:
Clap your hands, all you peoples; shout to God with loud songs of joy. For the LORD, the Most High, is awesome, a great king over all the earth.-Psalm 47

This rosary is made of beautiful gray Swarovski Crystal Pearls that coordinate perfectly with black crystal and glass foil beads. A unique sterling silver cross with heart embellishment make this a unique rosary.

name: Turquoise & Pearl Cross Rosary
description:
I sought the LORD, and he answered me, and delivered me from all my fears.-Psalm 34

Popular turquoise beads are complimented with unique pearl crosses.  This lovely keepsake would even make a beautiful necklace! Sterling silver cross and connector.

name: Carnelian Rosary
description:
I will extol you, my God and King, and bless your name forever and ever.-Psalm 145

Carnelian gemstones are a rich, lovely color accented with unique glass beads.  Detailed sterling silver cross is perfect for this collectable rosary.
(Hail Mary Beads = 6mm)
Length: 17"

name: Our Lady of Guadalupe
description: Religious pendant of Our Lady of Guadalupe with trio of funky glass beads.

name: Old World Virgin Mary Necklace
description: This large and gorgeous pendant is a conversation piece all on it's own.  We found a special artisan to cast an Old World medal and make a sterling silver version. It's gorgeous and unique with it's two sides, one of the Virgen Mary and the other, Jesus. Paired with large turquoise beads and sterling silver chain, it's truly an artful necklace.

name: Royal Faith
description: Brilliant faceted quartz beads are gorgeous in this garnet necklace.  Coordinated with a large sterling silver cross, this is a great addition to your wardrobe.

name: Multi-Stone Rosary Necklace
description: A mixture of beautiful gemstones sparkle against gold filled cross and connector.

name: St. Joseph Rosary
description:
Riverstone beads are paired with Picture Jasper (Our Fathers). Connector and crucifix in sterling silver. Great neutral rosary for male or female.
 (Hail Mary Beads = 7mm)
Length:  16"

name: St. Thomas More Rosary
description:
Gold Swarovski pearls with coordinating gold Swarovski crystal (Our Father beads) make a great keepsake rosary. All components including connector, spacers and cross are sterling silver.
Hail Mary beads are 6mm.
Length:  15"

name: Czech Glass Brown
description: Here is a great pair of earrings that I consider "neutral". The brown tones allow you to wear it with almost everything. The brown Czech glass beads fun and hang from handmade sterling silver ear wires.
